column1: Baby Barnaby's////The value you receive is top-notch with affordable prices
column3: and super quick orders.  My go-to is the Breakfast Plate and splitting a Blueberry Pancake with my girlfriend.  Other favorites include Migas
column4: Bob's Healthy Plate and Huevos Rancheros.  The coffee and fresh-squeezed OJ are a must with any order.
